---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Submit a Report">
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Submit Your Experience</h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-8">
      Share your peptide experience to help others make informed decisions. All submissions are reviewed before publication.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-8 p-6 bg-white border border-border rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-3">What Makes a Good Report</h2>
      <ul class="text-muted space-y-2">
        <li>Dosage & timing information</li>
        <li>Source Type (i.e. compounding pharmacy, research supplier, prescription (brand), etc. If purchased from a research supplier, please mention which one)</li>
        <li>Physical and mental effects felt during and after</li>
        <li>Medications, herbs, or supplements being taken</li>
        <li>Insights gained and/or problems encountered</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-3">An Unacceptable Report</h2>
      <ul class="text-muted space-y-2">
        <li>Has no paragraphs, punctuation, or capitalization, and poor spelling</li>
        <li>Describes what others will experience rather than your own</li>
        <li>Includes only a list of activities or nonspecific information</li>
        <li>The use of the term "SWIM" or similar</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 p-6 bg-neutral/10 border border-border rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-muted">
        Reports are used for education, harm-reduction, and research. Not all are published. Each is reviewed for writing quality, interest, and usefulness. Some are published within days, others can take a year or more to be reviewed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 p-6 bg-accent/5 border border-accent/20 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-3">Submission Form</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">
        Fill out the form below. Your report will be reviewed and you'll be notified when it's published.
      </p>

      <iframe
        data-tally-src="https://tally.so/embed/dWaerN?alignLeft=1&hideTitle=1&transparentBackground=1"
        loading="lazy"
        width="100%"
        height="1200"
        frameborder="0"
        marginheight="0"
        marginwidth="0"
        title="Peptide Experience Report"
      ></iframe>
      <script src="https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js" async></script>
    </section>

    <section class="text-sm text-muted space-y-4">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-ink">Privacy:</strong> Your email is only used to notify you of publication or ask follow-up questions. It's never published or shared.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong class="text-ink">Anonymity:</strong> Reports are published without identifying information unless you specifically request attribution.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong class="text-ink">Copyright Release:</strong> By submitting this report, you state that you are the author or owner of this text. You grant perpetual, non-revocable, international, transferrable, non-exclusive copyright to Pepowid. You grant permission for the full text (and/or excerpts) to be published on Pepowid.com used in promotional literature, scientific research, electronic and print publications, and other media types (video, audio, etc) of Pepowid's choosing. Reports may be edited to clarify text, remove personally identifying details, correct factual errors, or implement other editorial decisions including derivative works. Whenever report texts are used (not including aggregate data) attribution will be given to authors.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
